Package: autoreload.fix
Title: Provides two solutions to refresh a Shiny App
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Rene", "Vreede", , "vreede.rene@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: An addin is added to Rstudio which can be binded to a keyboard shortcut. Alternatively, a Shiny app can be launched which monitors file changes and updates the modified date of "app.R". This results in an automatic refresh of your app.
